General.Name: Stella International Holdings Limited
General.Description: Stella International Holdings Limited engages in development, manufacture, and sale of footwear products and leather goods in North America, the People's Republic of China, Europe, Asia, and internationally. The company operates in two segments, Manufacturing, and Retailing and Wholesaling. It is also involved in the holding of intellectual property rights; and the provision of secretary and accounting services. In addition, the company develops, manufactures, and sells handbags. It offers its products under the Stella Luna and What For brands. The company was founded in 1982 and is based in Kowloon, Hong Kong.
